Package: haplot
Type: Package
Title: short read variant visualizer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Ng", email = "tngthomasng@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package generates haplotype summary drawn from alignment
    and variant files, specifically from SAM and VCF files. Supported by R's shiny
    package, this dynamic generated graphical app serves the purpose of quality
    assessment of haplotype in various levels from individual basis to locus
    basis and to other labels. This app is also equipped with simple control panel
    allowing you to identify and remove any poor quality read.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
